&gt;&gt;Mark: Yeah.

00:06:40.460 --> 00:06:41.460
I don't know.

00:06:41.460 --> 00:06:44.250
I was automatically branded a rabble rouser

00:06:44.250 --> 00:06:45.250
&gt;&gt;Male Presenter: Yeah.

00:06:45.250 --> 00:06:46.250
That's like

00:06:46.250 --> 00:06:47.250
&gt;&gt;Mark: For doing two presentations.

00:06:47.250 --> 00:06:50.050
