&gt;&gt;Male Presenter: But in corporate, I mean,
the machinery of corporate.

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:35.220
&gt;&gt;Mark: It's like "The Book of the Five Rings."

00:07:35.220 --> 00:07:36.220
