00:07:37.220 --> 00:07:38.220
Kind of you know.

00:07:38.220 --> 00:07:39.220
Hit first.

00:07:39.220 --> 00:07:44.130
&gt;&gt;Male Presenter: So, but then you went into
TV animation but then it's still like you're,

00:07:44.130 --> 00:07:46.120
I would imagine that's starting from the ground
