There's so many potential ways to go on a
movie to show off a character or to describe

00:27:32.980 --> 00:27:36.080
this bit of information.

00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:37.550
But what's the right way?

00:27:37.550 --> 00:27:40.861
So that everything falls in line and the audience
is with you.

00:27:40.861 --> 00:27:41.861
You know?

00:27:41.861 --> 00:27:45.450
And this crying or laughing or on the edge
of their seats.

00:27:45.450 --> 00:27:46.780
So I love that problem.

00:27:46.780 --> 00:27:53.480
