And especially when we have these stories
that we ourselves dig and we're fans of.

00:28:00.340 --> 00:28:02.400
We're our harshest critics at Pixar.

00:28:02.400 --> 00:28:07.750
We put up the movie and storyboard reels and
we watch it.

00:28:07.750 --> 00:28:09.190
Everybody together.

00:28:09.190 --> 00:28:12.610
