and we do it again.

00:28:15.450 --> 00:28:17.440
And we do this constantly.

00:28:17.440 --> 00:28:23.090
Look at it because one of the lessons we learn
is that the proof is in the pudding.

00:28:23.090 --> 00:28:27.050
So you can talk about it all you want of what
the scene should be or what the story should

00:28:27.050 --> 00:28:29.419
be or the direction you should go.

00:28:29.419 --> 00:28:35.559
