00:28:59.500 --> 00:29:01.330
That's what we do all day.

00:29:01.330 --> 00:29:02.330
That's my job.

00:29:02.330 --> 00:29:06.350
Is to make a movie, a sucky movie.

00:29:06.350 --> 00:29:08.820
Look at it, and then gripe about it.

00:29:08.820 --> 00:29:11.580
Say "Man, they didn't have any motivation.

00:29:11.580 --> 00:29:13.910
That character was totally pointless in the
