stick it up and go "Less sucky.

00:29:22.419 --> 00:29:23.890
But still the ending I'm not.

00:29:23.890 --> 00:29:24.890
I don't care."

00:29:24.890 --> 00:29:28.320
And then you take it back and put it back
up and that's what we do.

