And we kind of go into it intellectually,
of what we need it to be about these characters.

00:30:22.050 --> 00:30:23.050
And their purpose.

00:30:23.050 --> 00:30:26.490
And how do we get the information to the audience?

00:30:26.490 --> 00:30:27.490
You know.

00:30:27.490 --> 00:30:31.830
In an economic and clear kinda way so that
they get all these ideas and the themes and

00:30:31.830 --> 00:30:33.900
they have an experience.

00:30:33.900 --> 00:30:36.670
That's a tall order.

00:30:36.670 --> 00:30:38.039
And it's trial and error.

00:30:38.039 --> 00:30:39.350
I mean the, I teach, too.

