What's the silver bullet?

00:30:48.640 --> 00:30:49.640
What's the secret?"

00:30:49.640 --> 00:30:52.140
I'm all, "The secret is just a lot of hard
work.

00:30:52.140 --> 00:30:57.120
It's banging your head against the concrete
until you make a hole in the wall and you

00:30:57.120 --> 00:30:58.120
