00:30:59.590 --> 00:31:03.830
You just have to try stuff on for size and
see that it doesn't work and try it again

00:31:03.830 --> 00:31:05.620
and try it again and try it again.

00:31:05.620 --> 00:31:13.950
Michelangelo talked about looking at the big
thing, square of marble and seeing the inside.

00:31:13.950 --> 00:31:16.620
We don't know what it is.

00:31:16.620 --> 00:31:19.650
We don't know what it is on the inside.

00:31:19.650 --> 00:31:25.380
We start chippin' at marble and then we ruin
that entire piece of marble going "I don't

00:31:25.380 --> 00:31:26.380
want David.

00:31:26.380 --> 00:31:27.380
I want.

00:31:27.380 --> 00:31:28.380
Oh, now I know what I want!"

00:31:28.380 --> 00:31:31.560
And we'd start on another piece of marble.

00:31:31.560 --> 00:31:32.799
I like to refer to it as alchemy.

00:31:32.799 --> 00:31:33.799
&gt;&gt;Male Presenter: Yeah.

