00:31:38.559 --> 00:31:39.559
Yes!

00:31:39.559 --> 00:31:40.559
How did we do that?

00:31:40.559 --> 00:31:41.559
I don't remember.

00:31:41.559 --> 00:31:43.320
" I have no idea what the formula was.

