time we go into another movie it's a new set

00:31:48.470 --> 00:31:49.470
of problems.

00:31:49.470 --> 00:31:50.679
It's a new set of variables.

00:31:50.679 --> 00:31:52.240
And it's different every time.

00:31:52.240 --> 00:31:55.980
I mean, there are.

00:31:55.980 --> 00:31:58.360
You have all these experiences from making
the movies.

