00:48:25.289 --> 00:48:27.319
With the lights done.

00:48:27.319 --> 00:48:28.769
And the set done.

00:48:28.769 --> 00:48:33.039
So we could look at it, constantly in context.

00:48:33.039 --> 00:48:36.509
So I think that is the next big step.

00:48:36.509 --> 00:48:39.799
&gt;&gt;male #2: So you mean like animating in a
