walkie talkies "OK, I'm comin' in now.

00:49:35.069 --> 00:49:36.069
Get ready.

00:49:36.069 --> 00:49:38.059
And, action!" and they do all the stuff just
like you do.

00:49:38.059 --> 00:49:41.039
So that's fantastic.

00:49:41.039 --> 00:49:43.579
And that's the kinda stuff that I wanna do.

00:49:43.579 --> 00:49:47.199
You know, using motion capture to get to those
answers quicker.

00:49:47.199 --> 00:49:48.199
Right?

00:49:48.199 --> 00:49:50.979
Because we can go down so many paths.

00:49:50.979 --> 00:49:57.190
When I was shooting live action on "John Carter"
we had spontaneity like this [snaps] all the

00:49:57.190 --> 00:49:58.190
time.

