This is, life is on the line.

00:50:10.170 --> 00:50:11.170
Come in you're totally defeated.

00:50:11.170 --> 00:50:12.170
Now, lone kid.

00:50:12.170 --> 00:50:13.170
That, that's' good.

00:50:13.170 --> 00:50:14.319
I got that one, come in totally defeated."

00:50:14.319 --> 00:50:17.289
And you're finding the scene in the context.

